ators in the stands.\", \"from\": 732, \"to\": 854, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Footage of his moment in the spotlight quickly went viral on X, with many hailing him as a \\\"hero\\\".\", \"from\": 855, \"to\": 953, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"READ MORE:Olympic cameramen officially warned over 'sexist' filming of women athletes    On person asked: \\\"Where's his gold medal, may I ask?!\\\"\", \"from\": 955, \"to\": 1098, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"One viewer quipped: \\\"The crowd cheers as a middle-aged man disrobes to just a speedo and dives in to recover the cap.\", \"from\": 1100, \"to\": 1217, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1178, \"end\": 1184, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Speedo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"speedo\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Speedo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Speedo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Words I thought I would not tweet this morning\\\".\", \"from\": 1218, \"to\": 1266, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Another said: \\\"Some guy in a Speedo just jumped into an Olympic pool to retrieve a swimmer's cap from the bottom of the pool.\", \"from\": 1268, \"to\": 1393, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1297, \"end\": 1303, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Speedo\", \"score\": 0.9999999551525899, \"rank\": 4.4847335483432595e-08, \"text\": \"Speedo\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Speedo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Speedo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I want that job is 2028 @Olympics\\\".\", \"from\": 1394, \"to\": 1429, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"DON'T MISS:Djokovic explains reason he 'did not connect' with Nadal after beating Spaniard  DON'T MISS:Olympic gymnast cries in pain as she forces body to continue with torn ligament  DON'T MISS:Frustrated Rafa Nadal shares what will make him quit tennis after Djokovic loss  the#oly